tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE election_results (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR,
    party_affiliation VARCHAR,
    votes_received INT
)

CREATE TABLE candidate_results (
    candidate_id INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(255),
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
    votes_received INT,
    election_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE ElectionResults (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(255),
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
    votes_received INT
);

CREATE TABLE VoterTurnout (
    election_id INT,
    voter_id INT,
    voter_name VARCHAR(255),
    precinct_id INT,
    vote_cast BOOLEAN,
    PRIMARY KEY (election_id, voter_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ElectionResults (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT NOT NULL,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
    votes_received INT
);
